comments: Birch (TOR) moves along the path of Booker (PHX) and some marginal contact occurs that the offensive player is able to continue through.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Siakam (TOR) and Ayton absorbs the marginal contact on the screen.
Bridges (PHX) brings a forearm to the body of Siakam (TOR) during the driving shot attempt but the contact is marginal and has no impact on the attempt at the rim.
VanVleet (TOR) moves alongside of Booker (PHX) on the perimeter and the body contact that occurs is marginal.
Booker (PHX) switches his pivot foot on the perimeter.
Payne (PHX) legally resumes his dribble after VanVleet (TOR) makes contact with the ball.

Payne (PHX) comes off of the screen and picks up his dribble. VanVleet (TOR) then reaches in and makes contact with the ball that dislodges it and Payne gathers the loose ball and proceeds to dribble.
Birch (TOR) moves into Payne (PHX) and the former's forearm makes contact with Payne's shoulder after the gather that impacts the driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) makes some marginal contact with the arm and body of Trent Jr. (TOR) after the release that does not impact his driving shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) briefly places and removes two hands from the body of Siakam (TOR) and there is no impact to SQBR during the drive.
Siakam (TOR) steps towards Ayton (PHX) and incidental foot to foot contact occurs as Ayton attempts to bring his right foot backwards and Siakam loses his balance.
Payne (PHX) commits a take foul on Trent Jr. (TOR).
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of VanVleet (TOR) and some marginal shoulder to shoulder contact occurs as Ayton is firming up during the screen.
Payne (PHX) commits a take foul on Trent Jr. (TOR).
